lass=\"repair-category\">\n<h3>MacBook Diagnostic Service</h3>\n<p>Comprehensive diagnostic identifying all hardware and software faults with a full written report.</p>\n<a class=\"repair-link\" href=\"/collections/macbook-diagnostic-prices\">Book Diagnostic Service →</a>\n</div>\n\n</section>",
